1
00:00:43,799 --> 00:00:44,880
Stay back!

2
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:45,520
Let go!

3
00:00:45,799 --> 00:00:46,679
Let go of me!

4
00:00:55,119 --> 00:00:55,560
Let go!

5
00:00:55,719 --> 00:00:56,600
Let go of me!

6
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:02,679
Qiuying.

7
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,159
Are you all right?

8
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:07,760
You killed him.

9
00:01:09,599 --> 00:01:10,560
Anyone who hurts you,

10
00:01:11,159 --> 00:01:12,120
I'll kill them on sight.

11
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:14,120
I won't spare a single one.

12
00:01:19,959 --> 00:01:21,599
So what do we do now?

13
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:23,159
We're in too deep to turn back now.

14
00:01:25,799 --> 00:01:26,879
Let me take you far away from here.

15
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,560
Okay.

16
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:43,599
You're eloping?

17
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,599
Since you've already seen us,

18
00:01:47,560 --> 00:01:48,799
if you're a real brother, let us go.

19
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,840
No way.

20
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:56,439
I'm not letting you two leave.

21
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,599
Why not?

22
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,680
Because you don't need to elope anymore.

23
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,199
The Brigade Commander's son...

24
00:02:09,560 --> 00:02:10,280
he kicked the bucket.

25
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,199
How did he die?

26
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:16,479
I just doubled his dose of medicine.

27
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,319
Who knew double the fun

28
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:19,520
meant kicking the bucket.

29
00:02:29,199 --> 00:02:30,319
Coming, coming, coming!

30
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:31,840
Coming!

31
00:02:32,159 --> 00:02:32,960
Stop banging!

32
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,479
You're Lao Jiugui, right?

33
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,159
Hurry!

34
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:38,080
She's been shot!

35
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:40,520
We don't take in the wounded here.

36
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:41,520
Only the dead.

37
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,159
Master.

38
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:43,520
It's me.

39
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:46,879
Xiao Lian.

40
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:48,520
Quick, quick, quick!

41
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:48,960
Get inside, hurry!

42
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:49,840
Hang in there!

43
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,120
What happened?

44
00:02:58,719 --> 00:02:59,719
Loosen her clothes.

45
00:03:28,319 --> 00:03:29,319
How is Xiao Lian?

46
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:31,439
Luckily, no bones were broken.

47
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:34,159
What on earth happened?

48
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:36,680
Let's talk over there.

49
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:38,120
Let Xiao Lian rest.

50
00:03:46,639 --> 00:03:47,439
Speak.

51
00:03:49,479 --> 00:03:50,439
My name is Zhou Xingbang.

52
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,159
I'm the liaison at Yin-Yang Crossing.

53
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:53,960
Last night, Li Chuanzhong,

54
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,240
who was stationed at Yin-Yang Crossing,

55
00:03:55,479 --> 00:03:56,520
suddenly launched an attack

56
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,360
on Clear Wind Stronghold.

57
00:03:58,199 --> 00:03:59,919
Xiao Lian was hurt

58
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,159
trying to protect me.

59
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,240
She had told me before

60
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,560
about Jigu Temple and you, Master.

61
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,319
So,

62
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,240
I brought her here.

63
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,439
What kind of nonsense is this?

64
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,919
Xiao Lian,

65
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,919
weren't you studying medicine in the provincial capital?

66
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,560
How did you end up at Clear Wind Stronghold?

67
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,000
And also,

68
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,560
who are you?

69
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:25,439
Why was Xiao Lian protecting you?

70
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,319
Master,

71
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,720
we're both Communists.

72
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,439
Xiao Lian, go and rest.

73
00:04:32,439 --> 00:04:32,839
What?

74
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:33,680
Comm...

75
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,839
Communists?

76
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:37,399
Yes.

77
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:39,040
We Communists

78
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,319
are an organization that fights

79
00:04:40,319 --> 00:04:41,399
for the common people.

80
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,439
Then why did you

81
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,720
go to Clear Wind Stronghold?

82
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,959
Aren't they all bandits there?

83
00:04:49,079 --> 00:04:49,920
Master,

84
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:51,360
although they're bandits,

85
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:52,199
they never harm

86
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:53,560
the common folk in the slightest.

87
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,120
When people are in trouble,

88
00:04:55,319 --> 00:04:56,519
they even lend a helping hand.

89
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:58,399
So the organization sent me

90
00:04:58,639 --> 00:04:59,720
and Liaison Zhou here

91
00:04:59,759 --> 00:05:00,879
to do ideological work

92
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:01,759
on their chief, Hu Jingchen.

93
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:02,839
We hope to win him over

94
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:03,920
to the people's side soon.

95
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:05,319
Then...

96
00:05:05,319 --> 00:05:06,120
then you...

97
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:08,279
You're not studying medicine

98
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:09,120
in the provincial capital anymore?

99
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:12,560
Master,

100
00:05:12,959 --> 00:05:15,519
medicine can only heal hundreds or thousands,

101
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:16,759
but the Communist Party

102
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,959
can save hundreds of millions

103
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:19,240
of toiling masses across the land.

104
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:22,160
No, wait...

105
00:05:22,199 --> 00:05:23,800
You've got me all confused.

106
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:26,399
I can't even understand you.

107
00:05:30,519 --> 00:05:31,519
He didn't coerce you?

108
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:33,519
I joined the Chinese Communist Party

109
00:05:33,519 --> 00:05:34,600
of my own free will.

110
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:41,600
Alright.

111
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:43,439
If you

112
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:45,279
joined of your own accord,

113
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,160
then your Master

114
00:05:49,759 --> 00:05:50,839
will support you.

115
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:01,480
That worthless son of mine

116
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:03,439
If he were half the man I am,

117
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,040
he wouldn't have ended up

118
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,439
in this state today.

119
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:11,439
Each person has their own fate.

120
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:14,199
Please accept my condolences, Brigade Commander.

121
00:06:15,680 --> 00:06:16,120
It's nothing.

122
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,240
Just the smoke in my eyes.

123
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:19,759
All right, all right.

124
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:20,720
You may all leave.

125
00:06:25,959 --> 00:06:26,639
In that case,

126
00:06:27,079 --> 00:06:28,160
I'll have to trouble you, Priestess,

127
00:06:28,279 --> 00:06:30,120
to perform rites for my son for seven days.

128
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,240
Of course.

129
00:06:32,519 --> 00:06:33,319
Reporting, Brigade Commander.

130
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:35,199
Clear Wind Stronghold has been fully taken.

131
00:06:35,680 --> 00:06:37,439
The bandit chief Hu Jingchen has been killed.

132
00:06:38,920 --> 00:06:40,000
That counts as

133
00:06:40,279 --> 00:06:41,279
some good news.

134
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,759
But while we were clearing

135
00:06:42,759 --> 00:06:43,720
out Clear Wind Stronghold,

136
00:06:43,839 --> 00:06:45,439
we found many subversive books.

137
00:06:47,879 --> 00:06:48,839
Please take a look.

138
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,560
Communists?

139
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,079
Yes, sir.

140
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,839
According to some of the bandits' confessions,

141
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:57,439
they said

142
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,759
there are two Communists

143
00:06:58,759 --> 00:07:00,160
who've been living at Clear Wind Stronghold.

144
00:07:00,600 --> 00:07:01,319
Where are they then?

145
00:07:02,879 --> 00:07:03,959
When we swept the battlefield,

146
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,959
we found no trace of them.

147
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:09,160
Then they must have escaped.

148
00:07:09,839 --> 00:07:10,240
Quick!

149
00:07:10,879 --> 00:07:12,279
Lock down the entire city immediately.

150
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,519
Search every inch of the city,

151
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,720
and bring those two back to me!

152
00:07:15,199 --> 00:07:15,560
Yes, sir.

153
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:20,680
Once I catch those two,

154
00:07:21,439 --> 00:07:22,720
I'll be promoted to Division Commander.

155
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,079
Master.

156
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,079
When the revolution succeeds,

157
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,360
we'll definitely come back to see you.

158
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,040
All right.

159
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:35,079
Master,

160
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,279
Here's hoping for an early victory,

161
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:37,759
so our family of four

162
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,639
can reunite soon.

163
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:41,560
Master,

164
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:42,519
Please take care of yourself.

165
00:07:42,879 --> 00:07:44,439
And look after Xiao Lian for me.

166
00:07:45,759 --> 00:07:46,399
Don't worry.

167
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:56,480
We can't leave now.

168
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:58,800
What's wrong?

169
00:07:58,879 --> 00:07:59,560
Let's talk inside.

170
00:07:59,639 --> 00:08:00,199
What happened?

171
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:01,199
Go, go, go.

172
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:02,079
Talk inside.

173
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,279
Hurry, come in.

174
00:08:03,279 --> 00:08:04,199
Come in, come in.

175
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,360
What's going on?

176
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,120
They're checking strictly at the gates.

177
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,160
Stopping everyone who passes.

178
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:15,959
I saw the Cui family's

179
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:17,160
second son, the soldier, say

180
00:08:17,399 --> 00:08:18,399
they're hunting revolutionaries.

181
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,600
They must be after me and Liaison Zhou.

182
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,279
Outside there are

183
00:08:24,279 --> 00:08:25,439
wanted posters of you two.

184
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,399
Well...

185
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:31,199
let's just stay home for now.

186
00:08:32,799 --> 00:08:33,600
Wait and see what happens.

187
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:34,600
All right?

188
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:35,440
No.

189
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:37,600
We need to think of another way.

190
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,559
If I stay here,

191
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:39,519
I'm afraid I'll drag you down.

192
00:08:39,519 --> 00:08:40,879
Sit down and stay right here.

193
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,440
Quit trying to be a hero.

194
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,120
Put it down.

195
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,200
I can't stop you anymore.

196
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,519
Xingbang.

197
00:08:50,679 --> 00:08:52,679
Everything you've said these past days,

198
00:08:53,159 --> 00:08:53,879
I've also

199
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,080
taken it to heart.

200
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,639
Also,

201
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,600
this thing here,

202
00:09:00,080 --> 00:09:01,480
the day Xiao Lian got hurt,

203
00:09:02,279 --> 00:09:03,799
it fell out of your pocket.

204
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:04,639
I read it too.

205
00:09:06,639 --> 00:09:07,720
I just want to ask,

206
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:11,559
can you really achieve

207
00:09:11,559 --> 00:09:13,200
what's written in that book?

208
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,279
Master,

209
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,759
that's exactly what we're fighting for.

210
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:17,360
To achieve this goal, we would

211
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,240
sacrifice everything,

212
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:19,279
even our lives.

213
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,000
No.

214
00:09:20,519 --> 00:09:21,360
Don't sacrifice your life.

215
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:24,200
If anyone's gonna sacrifice, it's me.

216
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:27,799
All right.

217
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:30,759
If it really can be like the book says,

218
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,480
count your Master in.

219
00:09:35,519 --> 00:09:36,720
Master,

220
00:09:37,039 --> 00:09:38,279
you're truly great.

221
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,639
Watch your wound, watch your wound!

222
00:09:45,840 --> 00:09:47,159
It's been three days now.

223
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,759
City gates blocked, mountains searched.

224
00:09:49,080 --> 00:09:50,240
Where did those two run off to?

225
00:09:51,399 --> 00:09:51,840
Dongsheng.

226
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:53,159
Thank you.

227
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,320
What are you thanking me for?

228
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:55,279
Thank you for saving

229
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:56,120
my life and Qiuying's.

230
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:58,039
Wait...

231
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,720
Are we even talking about the same thing?

232
00:10:03,240 --> 00:10:03,840
Boss.

233
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,279
Let's take a break.

234
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:07,440
We've been walking all day.

235
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,600
Get that uniform and cap

236
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,519
on properly, all of you.

237
00:10:12,519 --> 00:10:13,480
Look at the state of you.

238
00:10:13,840 --> 00:10:14,720
Do you even look like a soldier?

239
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:15,720
Thought you were still

240
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:16,679
back in your bandit days.

241
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:19,000
Hurry up.

242
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:25,240
What was the Brigade Commander thinking,

243
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:27,519
letting these surrendered bandits join us.

244
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,360
Just using them for show.

245
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:31,399
Oh, right.

246
00:10:31,399 --> 00:10:32,480
Jigu Temple is just up ahead.

247
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:33,799
Good chance to drop by

248
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:34,639
and see Master and Auntie Xiaoling.

249
00:10:34,679 --> 00:10:35,159
Sure.

250
00:10:35,480 --> 00:10:36,279
We can grab some water too.

251
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:36,799
Let's go.

252
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:41,879
Where are you from?

253
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:42,799
Sichuan.

254
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:43,840
A Sichuan fellow.

255
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,039
Xiao Lian.

256
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,919
Do you have a thing for young Zhou?

257
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:54,000
That won't do.

258
00:10:54,679 --> 00:10:56,120
You grew up with your big brother.

259
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:57,399
You can't go falling for someone else.

260
00:10:58,039 --> 00:10:59,639
Auntie Xiaoling, who do you mean?

261
00:11:00,120 --> 00:11:01,240
Your brother Dongsheng.

262
00:11:01,679 --> 00:11:02,399
Him?

263
00:11:03,120 --> 00:11:05,039
He just loafs around all day.

264
00:11:05,360 --> 00:11:06,879
Even dogs run the other way when they see him.

265
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:08,000
That's no way to talk about your brother.

266
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,919
Auntie Xiaoling,

267
00:11:10,039 --> 00:11:11,360
I've always seen him as my brother.

268
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,879
How could I ever marry him?

269
00:11:13,279 --> 00:11:13,919
I don't care.

270
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,360
We're not letting

271
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,519
this go to some outsider.

272
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,879
Auntie Xiaoling,

273
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:18,919
why are you even more

274
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:19,960
old-fashioned than my Master?

275
00:11:21,399 --> 00:11:22,200
What?

276
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,480
What did I say?

277
00:11:24,240 --> 00:11:25,120
That Lao Jiugui...

278
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,600
he's not so bad either, is he?

279
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:32,080
Xingbang.

280
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:34,519
You really

281
00:11:34,519 --> 00:11:36,080
don't take a single thing from the people.

282
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:39,720
It's not just toward the people.

283
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,519
Within our ranks,

284
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,519
we forbid beating or cursing soldiers,

285
00:11:43,759 --> 00:11:44,600
or skimming their pay.

286
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,600
Officers and soldiers are equal.

287
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,039
That's wonderful.

288
00:11:52,559 --> 00:11:53,679
I'm too old now.

289
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:56,120
I missed out on the good times.

290
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:57,960
Master, listen to yourself.

291
00:11:58,200 --> 00:12:00,120
You're stronger than ever, if you ask me.

292
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:07,120
Coming!

293
00:12:10,679 --> 00:12:11,720
Auntie Xiaoling,

294
00:12:11,879 --> 00:12:12,799
Shuisheng's here.

295
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:13,759
Hello, Auntie Xiaoling.

296
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:14,519
Auntie Xiaoling,

297
00:12:14,519 --> 00:12:15,440
got anything to eat or drink?

298
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,600
We're starving.

299
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:17,679
My apprentice.

300
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:18,679
Don't worry.

301
00:12:20,279 --> 00:12:21,200
Lao Jiugui,

302
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:22,399
look who's here.

303
00:12:22,559 --> 00:12:23,039
Dongsheng.

304
00:12:23,039 --> 00:12:23,559
Master.

305
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:24,720
Shuisheng came too.

306
00:12:26,519 --> 00:12:27,159
Xiao Lian.

307
00:12:27,759 --> 00:12:28,240
Brother.

308
00:12:31,399 --> 00:12:32,519
Those two grew up together.

309
00:12:33,639 --> 00:12:34,799
That one's my apprentice.

310
00:12:34,799 --> 00:12:35,360
Hasn't grown an inch.

311
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,120
You silly girl.

312
00:12:36,879 --> 00:12:37,720
Don't touch my head.

313
00:12:37,759 --> 00:12:38,919
Too much of that and I won't grow tall.

314
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,600
You came back without telling me?

315
00:12:42,639 --> 00:12:43,080
Report!

316
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:45,080
This Zhou Xingbang is a Communist.

317
00:12:45,159 --> 00:12:46,159
And so is this woman.

318
00:12:49,039 --> 00:12:49,519
You...

319
00:12:57,279 --> 00:12:57,840
Dongsheng

320
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,120
What is the meaning of this?

321
00:13:00,039 --> 00:13:01,120
They're Communists.

322
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:02,639
I don't care who she is.

323
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,600
All I know is she's my sister.

324
00:13:06,639 --> 00:13:07,960
Anyone who dares hurt her,

325
00:13:08,159 --> 00:13:09,519
even if the King of Heaven shows up,

326
00:13:09,879 --> 00:13:10,840
I won't hold back.
